==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zionism
<hw>Zi"on*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Zion</ets> +
<ets>-ism</ets>.]</ety> <def>Among the Jews, a theory, plan, or movement
for colonizing their own race in Palestine, the land of Zion, or, if
that is impracticable, elsewhere, either for religious or nationalizing
purposes; -- called also <altname>Zion movement</altname>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Zi"on*ist</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> -- <wf>Zi`on*is"tic</wf>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

